{"tid":840262,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"銀魂半隻腳上咗神枱 家下又跌返落嚟","createTime":"2018-09-28T14:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T11:33:01.000Z","uid":187227,"like":10,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3519670fb818d29156e42b6a284b67517c2aa7f1","tid":840262,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"以下一切都以動畫為基礎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前嘅銀魂會覺得：屌乜咁快完又要等一個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅銀魂悶撚到仆街 只係想咋咋臨睇完<br />\n<br />\n由銀之魂篇已經唔知想點 啲劇情扎腳布咁又長又尋<br />\n<br />\n屌好心猩猩畫返日常啦 佢根本handle唔到咁長嘅主線<br />\n<br />\n傾城篇 暗殺篇呢啲故事結構簡單 主旨清楚 而且篇幅短 正正就係咁先吸引到人<br />\n<br />\n而家佢根本眼高手低兩頭唔到岸 想寫黑暗野又未夠喉 想寫角色多線交叉又寫到笠笠亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n比銀魂入土為安啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987db088049cfcec124d597f6db98d40d40bcccf","tid":840262,"uid":201662,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3519670fb818d29156e42b6a284b67517c2aa7f1","tid":840262,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:56: